LOVE UNLEASHED CHARITY VIRTUAL BENEFIT CONCERT 2023 is Presented by JEHOVAH SHALOM ACAPELLA. The Show is Produced By DC Productions U.S.A and Directed By DAVIES CHIRWA.

#jehovahshalom #loveunleashed #channelatv #jehovahshalomacapella #theclarioncallzambia #thokoza #chinedugboof #samsam

Welcome to "Love Unleashed," a concert with a special cause. JSA Music Group and special guests including THE CLARION CALL ZAMBIA, THOKOZA, TAD WORKU, GINEDU GBOOF featuring SAM SAM are coming together to turn melodies into meals, aiming to feed 100+ families in Kampala slums. Your support is the harmony we will resonate long after the music stops.
